textBox.richText: Member of the biometric team from Sep 2011 to Dec 2015. PhD on face anti-spoofing. Involved in the project TABULA RASA. Ivana Chingovska completed her master degree at the Faculty of Electrical Engineering and Information Technology at the Ss. Cyril and Methodius University in Skopje, Macedonia, in 2011. Since 2008 she has been working as a junior teaching and lab assistant and as a researcher at the Digital Image Processing team at her faculty. She has completed student internships at the technical universities in Lisbon, Madrid and Cardiff, working on various computer vision projects.
